**Why consider mbuzz:** Dreamdata shows attribution. mbuzz lets you compare 8 models side-by-side and build custom logic. *Disclosure: mbuzz is our product.*

Server-side tracking captures 95%+ of touchpoints (vs client-side tools losing 30-40% to ad blockers). 7 attribution models with side-by-side comparison — see how First Touch, Last Touch, Markov Chain, Shapley Value, and others credit the same deal differently. Custom rules via DSL let you define B2B-specific logic. LTV attribution tracks expansion and renewals back to acquisition source.

**10-minute setup** with native SDKs for [Rails](https://rubygems.org/gems/mbuzz), [Django](https://pypi.org/project/mbuzz), [Laravel](https://packagist.org/packages/mbuzz/mbuzz-php), and [Node.js](https://www.npmjs.com/package/mbuzz). Pricing: Free tier, then $29-299/mo.

